---
import SiteLayout from '../layouts/SiteLayout.astro';
---

<SiteLayout
  title="Contact | RustZen"
  description="Contact RustZen support for Zen Clear questions, billing, refunds, and license help."
>
  <main class="legal-page">
    <article class="legal-document">
      <p class="eyebrow">Contact</p>
      <h1>Contact RustZen</h1>
      <p>
        For Zen Clear support, billing questions, refund requests, license
        activation issues, or privacy requests, email
        <a href="mailto:support@rustzen.dev">support@rustzen.dev</a>.
      </p>

      <h2>What To Include</h2>
      <p>
        For license or billing requests, include the email used at checkout,
        your Creem order or subscription reference if available, your app
        version, and a short description of the issue.
      </p>

      <h2>Product</h2>
      <p>
        Zen Clear is a native macOS cleanup app for developer, AI, container,
        and system caches. Zen Clear Pro is the annual $10/year paid
        subscription for cleanup and license-backed features on up to three
        devices. Scan and preview are available before cleanup.
      </p>
    </article>
  </main>
</SiteLayout>
